íŸ@fb625c9981e9d873385ee60be73a128c0b2b630d0f5a9f89018e5d390b99bec7⁄_Title: title: bytes length
Path: Examples
Content:
Return the length of a binary.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[1F FF AA AB] | bytes length
4

```
Return the lengths of multiple binaries.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [0x[1F FF AA AB] 0x[1F]] | bytes length
